:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502050117-->
:::'''Jingzhai:''' I'm now in charge of a matrix at the Matrix of Prescience... My jobs include making divination inferences and recording the changes.
:::'''Jingzhai:''' I'm afraid I can't disclose the details of the matrix as it involves confidential information about the Divination Commission.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
